                     <interp inst="t17210419-10-off55" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17210419-10-off55" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing two half Guineas
            </rs>, the Money of 
               
